## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="01f64-102"><xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.WebHttpElement> è un sottotipo di <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.BehaviorExtensionElement> che può essere utilizzato per includere <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebHttpBehavior> in un endpoint tramite configurazione.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="01f64-102">The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.WebHttpElement> is a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.BehaviorExtensionElement> sub-type that can be used to include the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebHttpBehavior> on an endpoint through configuration.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="01f64-103">Il comportamento <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebHttpBehavior>, quando utilizzato insieme all'associazione <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpBinding>, consente di utilizzare il modello di programmazione Web per un servizio [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/includes/indigo1-md.md)].</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="01f64-103">The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WebHttpBehavior> behavior, when used in conjunction with the <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpBinding> binding, enables the Web programming model for a [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/includes/indigo1-md.md)] service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="01f64-104">Si noti che <xref:System.ServiceModel.Web.WebServiceHost> aggiunge automaticamente questo comportamento agli endpoint che utilizzano <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpBinding>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="01f64-104">Note that the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Web.WebServiceHost> automatically adds this behavior to endpoints that use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.WebHttpBinding>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="01f64-105">L'esempio restituisce il tipo <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.WebHttpElement>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="01f64-105">This sample returns the type <xref:System.ServiceModel.Configuration.WebHttpElement>.</span></span>  
  
```  
using System;  
using System.ServiceModel;  
using System.ServiceModel.Web;  
using System.ServiceModel.Configuration;  
  
    class Program  
    {  
        static void Main(string[] args)  
        {  
            WebHttpElement webHttpElement = new WebHttpElement();  
            Console.WriteLine("The type is: {0}", webHttpElement.BehaviorType);  
            Console.WriteLine("Press <ENTER> to terminate the program.");  
            Console.ReadLine();  
        }  
    }  
```

  
  
